OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778230885
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man killed in
OL,4,Chit-and-run as driver jailed
OL,6,FThe family of a 76-year-old man who
OL,7,Fdied in a hit and run collision in
OL,8,FBristol has said the impact of his
OL,9,Fdeath is "greater than anyone could
OL,10,Fever know".
OL,12,FJames Randall, 34, was speeding and
OL,13,Fusing his mobile phone when he hit
OL,14,FPhilip Cole with his van on Ilminster
OL,15,FAvenue on 18 January 2024.
OL,17,FThe 34-year-old pled guilty to causing
OL,18,Fdeath by dangerous driving when he
OL,19,Fappeared at Bristol Crown Court in
OL,20,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
