PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778230885
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man killed in
OL,4,Chit-and-run as driver jailed
OL,6,FOn 20 April, he was sentenced to five
OL,7,Fyears and six months in prison and
OL,8,Fgiven a 93-month driving ban.
OL,10,FHe will also need to take an extended
OL,11,Fdriving test before he can receive his
OL,12,Flicence again.
OL,14,FMr Cole died of his injuries five
OL,15,Fweeks after the collision. Randall
OL,16,Ffled the scene in his van, which was
OL,17,Flater discovered on Narroway Road.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778230885
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man killed in
OL,4,Chit-and-run as driver jailed
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police reviewed CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage to track the car's route and
OL,8,Farrested Randall three days after the
OL,9,Fcollision.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the sentencing hearing, Mr
OL,12,FCole's niece said: "It is impossible
OL,13,Ftrying to put into words the impact of
OL,14,FPhilip's death. Sitting at his side
OL,15,Fwatching the constant care needed, the
OL,16,Fglimmer of hope as he made it through
OL,17,Feach day, only to be given the
OL,18,Fheartbreaking news five weeks later
OL,19,Fthat there was nothing else the
OL,20,Fdoctors could do.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778230885
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man killed in
OL,4,Chit-and-run as driver jailed
OL,6,F"Witnessing end of life care of a
OL,7,Floved one has been the hardest thing
OL,8,Fwe have had to deal with. The haunting
OL,9,Fmemories forever with us. It feels
OL,10,Flike we have been living in a
OL,11,Fnightmare every day since.
OL,13,F"Our lives were completely turned
OL,14,Fupside down on the 18th January 2024
OL,15,Fand will never be the same again."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
