CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1778230885
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man killed in
OL,4,Chit-and-run as driver jailed
OL,6,FDC Jakob Meikle, the investigating
OL,7,Fofficer for Avon and Somerset Police,
OL,8,Fsaid: "A small justice has been done
OL,9,Fin the sentencing of a reckless and
OL,10,Fcowardly individual who attempted to
OL,11,Favoid the consequences of his actions
OL,12,Fand the damage he caused Philip's
OL,13,Ffamily.
OL,15,F"They will forever be impacted by this
OL,16,Fincident and my thoughts go out to
OL,17,Fthem."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
